{"tid":1289194,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地就好似玩緊黑暗中對話咁","createTime":"2019-07-06T03:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T03:54:42.000Z","uid":208731,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d29ec89ab92cfabe66d92b0bf0e1640a5461822","tid":1289194,"uid":208731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"香港依家就好似玩黑暗中對話咁<br />\n好似咩都睇唔到<br />\n好似咩都唔知要摸下摸下<br />\n過程會撞到跌倒<br />\n會辛苦會難受<br />\n<br />\n不過即使係咁<br />\n香港人唔好放棄<br />\n真係唔到放棄<br />\n我地知道有終點有曙光的<br />\n所以唔好停<br />\n一停就輸<br />\n所以要keep住向前行<br />\n同兄弟隊友一齊行<br />\n互相支援鼓勵<br />\n不論你係黑暗中向前衝又好<br />\n幫手摸下搵下路又好<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係一齊繼續向前行<br />\n <br />\n強權終會倒下<br />\n<br />\n天佑我城"},{"pid":"ca16dc8cb809d46ffb468aca165d48d989cb6fd9","tid":1289194,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykF0iKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykF0iKu.png&h=e791e1a6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4VWBwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4VWBwa.png&h=c69769d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBEXk4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBEXk4h.png&h=add7d72c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFtk3bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFtk3bc.png&h=12717881&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZF7Jbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZF7Jbd.png&h=011957c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXh5pz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXh5pz.png&h=517cf7bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtXh5uE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtXh5uE.png&h=774ac168&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygiEzhX